                  </persName>
            . I found the snuffer-tray and watch in the same place where the pocket-book was found at the same time.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence, The sweep asked me to go to Brentford with him. He threw a stone at me which made me run.</p>
               <p>GEORGE HULL. I am an officer. The house is in the parish of St. Mary Abbot, Kensington.</p>
